    "description": "The reformulated hypoallergenic Almay Clear Complexion Makeup for sensitive skin does not just cover and fight acne, it supports skin health too. Ideal for acne prone skin types, oily skin, and combination skin, the creamy multitasking foundation with medium, buildable coverage helps treat acne breakouts, hides imperfections, and leaves skin with a flawless, soft matte finish that lasts all day\u2014no caking up. The difference is that now, the non comedogenic (won\u2019t clog pores!) liquid acne foundation is powered by a skin balancing formula of 1% salicylic acid, prebiotics, and aloe vera for skin that looks clarified, healthier, and calm. The amount of salicylic acid\u2014the magic acne fighting ingredient\u2014was reduced to treat and help prevent future breakouts without drying out skin. Added prebiotics nourish a healthy skin barrier for a well balanced complexion. Aloe vera was also introduced into the mix for its hydrating properties, which help soothe and calm signs of irritation. Formulated without added parabens, phthalates, SLS, mineral oil, DMDM Hydantoin, formaldehydes, Triclosan, and palm oils. Suitable for sensitive skin. As always, hypoallergenic. Dermatologist tested. Clean. Cruelty free. Fragrance free.",
